@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. 회원별 계좌 목록 조회
# Auth.http 로그인 후 발급된 auth_token 필요
# @name getAccounts
GET {{host}}/api/accounts/member/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

> {% client.global.set("withdraw_account_id", response.body.data[0].id); %}

### 2. 특정 계좌 상세 조회
GET {{host}}/api/accounts/{{withdraw_account_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json